snippet.title: infinite Sky Dev Log 004
snippet.description:
Lots of new stuff going on here! There's new music (it's just rough and unrefined for now but gets the idea) . There have been updates to the combat system that are hard to see but effect the feel of game-play. Lastly there are also item drops now. 

Alright until next post have a good one!
